335
00:23:19,946 --> 00:23:26,619
There is no escape

336
00:23:26,619 --> 00:23:34,727
I place my sorrow upon a bird in the sky

337
00:23:34,727 --> 00:23:38,993
And I'll let it fly

338
00:23:43,603 --> 00:23:47,407
This place is ephemeral

339
00:23:47,407 --> 00:23:58,384
An eternity that binds me

340
