343
00:24:30,984 --> 00:24:32,919
Your name?

344
00:24:32,919 --> 00:24:34,754
Minami Shibuya.

345
00:24:34,754 --> 00:24:39,092
Are you really sure?
She's your friend, isn't she?

346
00:24:39,092 --> 00:24:40,894
She was my friend.

347
00:24:40,894 --> 00:24:43,796
I thought she was my one
and only true friend,

348
00:24:43,796 --> 00:24:46,366
but after what she did...

349
00:24:46,366 --> 00:24:47,800
I can't forgive her.

350
00:24:47,800 --> 00:24:49,869
Your wish?

351
00:24:49,869 --> 00:24:52,372
Banish her to Hell for me!

